# Motivation

- A debug feature providing an interface through which an application is notified when task switching occurs.
- This can be useful when profiling system activity, active tasks, number of calls per task ...

# Goals

- Extend task switching mechanism such that if the external task profiling hook is provided, it will be called with from and to ids of switching tasks.

# Release Impact: Minor

# Test Plan

- All regression tests pass
